"For example:"
msgstr "O senhor instalou pelo menos uma extensão que fornece um `IdentityProvider` com base no nome de usuário e na senha. Por exemplo:"

#: _guides/security-basic-authentication-howto.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "xref:security-jpa.adoc[Quarkus Security Jakarta Persistence extensions (`security-jpa` or `security-jpa-reactive`)]"
msgstr "xref:security-jpa.adoc[Extensões do Quarkus Security Jakarta Persistence (security-jpa ou security-jpa-reactive)]"

#: _guides/security-basic-authentication-howto.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "xref:security-properties.adoc[Elytron security properties file extension `(quarkus-elytron-security-properties-file)`]"
msgstr "xref:security-properties.adoc[Extensão do arquivo Elytron security properties (quarkus-elytron-security-properties-file)]"

#: _guides/security-basic-authentication-howto.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "xref:security-jdbc.adoc[Elytron security JDBC extension `(quarkus-elytron-security-jdbc)`]"
